          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Data Collection</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Generally, visiting the Website does not require personal data. When you use the Website, non-personal data (e.g., your internet service provider, pages visited, or time spent on the site) may be collected to enhance user experience and improve services. This data does not identify you personally.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Personal data is collected only when you voluntarily provide it—such as submitting inquiries, requesting quotations, or using contact forms. By using the Website and providing personal data, you consent to its processing for marketing, communication, and insurance-consulting purposes.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Cookies</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            The Website uses cookies—small text files stored on your device—to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
            <li>Recognize returning visitors</li>
            <li>Remember preferences</li>
            <li>Analyze usage patterns</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Some cookies are session-based and expire when you close your browser; others persist to streamline future visits. You may configure your browser to block or delete cookies; however, this may impact the functionality of certain Website features.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Use and Disclosure of Personal Data</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Your personal data will be used exclusively:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
            <li>To provide requested services (e.g., insurance quotes, consultations)</li>
            <li>To respond to inquiries</li>
            <li>To facilitate insurance-related advice through authorized partners</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We do not sell personal data to third parties for research or advertising. Where necessary, data is shared with authorized insurance intermediaries and partners—all of whom are bound by strict confidentiality and data protection laws.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Right of Access and Rectification</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            You have the right, at any time, to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
            <li>Request information about the personal data we hold</li>
            <li>Request rectification, restriction, or deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Obtain data portability, according to Swiss and applicable international law</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            To exercise these rights, please email hello@expat-savvy.ch.
          </p>

